{"tid":1867303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來連登仔反共反咗咁多年，都唔知中國共產黨最驚係咩，笑死人","createTime":"2020-02-07T06:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T09:30:02.000Z","uid":57376,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"68660bc744ff4880716d45364551de1c0c0d1873","tid":1867303,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:25:27.000Z","msg":"好多人都仲睇唔清<br />\n中共由建國至今，未驚過天災，未驚過瘟疫，未驚過大飢荒，反正全部有晒經驗，人我又大把，死幾多都唔怕<br />\n國際圍堵我可以鎖國，打仗我唔怕死人，經濟崩潰我可以推倒重來，奴隸我大把，幾窮都唔會差過北韓<br />\n<br />\n但有樣野中共日防夜防，防足六十年，無所不用其極咁防，又網軍五毛又防火長城又人臉監控，嗰樣野叫做「人權覺醒」<br />\n因為中共最怕最怕嘅係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無奴隸用</span><br />\n<br />\n然後宜家連登仔係度爭拗應唔應該鼓吹班奴隸反抗主人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79996477b087c9c66eca62618976c3643179a1b8","tid":1867303,"uid":20272,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:28:30.000Z","msg":"緊要要有咁大吹咁大啦<br />\n<br />\n不過唔好當咗班支那種係手足就得<br />\n佢地護旗撐警永遠都係死不足惜<br />\n但要拉攏同利用佢地"},{"pid":"5a27024541beaf19b853b1509d5785a724981035","tid":1867303,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:31:01.000Z","msg":"醫護<br />\n<br />\n投票時間至1630🟥<br />\n<br />\n要6000會員投票呀‼️‼️‼️‼️<br />\n快啲出黎啦‼️‼️‼️<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n【延長醫護罷工計劃投票】<br />\n投票截至今日下午四半時<br />\n只限會員<br />\n￼<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf_VSITn5RwMPGSP36LWB06DYnns4wnLlsHi2-PBumry03GHw/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSf_VSITn5RwMPGSP36LWB06DYnns4wnLlsHi2-PBumry03GHw%2Fviewform&d=uFnVTFPFh